INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES ('1', '5', '5', 'Get your own Armenian dresses', 'get-your-own-armenian-dresses-1', 'Parev,\r\n\r\nI\'ve been studying fashion in a design school in Yerevan. Fashion has been my passion ever since I\'ve been 12 years old. I hope you like my creations, they are unique, traditional but occasionally casual, which means you can wear them as often as you like while being sure you will stand out!', 'project_11387706827Untitled-2.jpg', null, '', '', '<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>Hello!</h3>\r\n<p>My curiosity for fashion was ignited when I worked next to the main design school in Yerevan. Every day, I felt like I should be on the opposite side of the street where I could study and know all the tips on how to do my own line of clothing. I started taking weekend classes and eventually in 2010 I had enough savings to take up fashion school full time.<br /> Now with what I learnt and my Armenian roots, I am willing to develop a full cloth line of traditional Armenian clothes. My approach to fashion is that anything can be put on anyone. But only if you have your own identity. My clothes are authentic but easy to wear more casually if you mix with other styles.</p>\r\n<p>Please have a look at this small video: I can reproduce most of the dresses there! But for this I need $2000 to allow for the buying of expensive fabric.</p>\r\n<p><br /> <iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/eGBpKSZuFRM?feature=player_detailpage\" width=\"596\" height=\"335\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>Why $2000?</h3>\r\n<p>With this money I will be able to handcraft most of the outfits in the video. I will have then a full line of clothing that I will be able to send throughout the world.</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>What you will get in return for your support:</h3>\r\n<p>If my funding goal of $2000 is reached, I will reward you with the dress on the picture.</p>\r\n<p>There is only one size I can do but you can wear it loose. This means it can fit many sizes. There is a lot of work involved for every single piece.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Support me</strong> <strong>and you will make many of your neighbors jealous</strong> with this unique garment!</p>\r\n<p>So far I do not do the shoes but I can change my mind for early backers!<br /> Any questions or remark, please ask me directly! Thanks :) Bachigs. <br /> &nbsp;</p>', '398', '{\"id\":\"398##Yerevan##AM\",\"name\":\"Yerevan, AM\"}', 'AM', '', 'no_of_days', '13', '1389881211', '', '0', '1397260799', '2000', '0', '0', null, '0', '0', '1', '1387708995', '1', null, '1', '0', '1386865355', '1387708989', null, '0', '0', '0', '1396131980');
INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES ('5', '2', '11', 'my new brand new test', 'my-new-brand-new-test', 'Hi this is underwater short movie I am working on please join', 'project_51387317287Untitled-1.jpg', null, '', '', '<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/sVq_zBDhhEw?feature=player_detailpage\" width=\"568\" height=\"319\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>My curiosity for fashion was ignited when I worked next to the main design school in Yerevan. Every day, I felt like I should be on the opposite side of the street where I could study and know all the tips on how to do my own line of clothing. I started taking weekend classes and eventually in 2010 I had enough savings to take up fashion school full time.</p>\r\n<p>Now with what I learnt and my Armenian roots, I am willing to develop a full cloth line of traditional Armenian clothes. My approach to fashion is that anything can be put on anyo<img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"/img/stuff/497dd74984352638b15c6ceec0548053.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"253\" height=\"553\" />ne. But only if you have your own identity. My clothes are authentic but easy to wear.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Please have a look at this small video where I saw some people in France wearing the same type of clothes. See how they are all having fun?</p>\r\n<p>With my clothes you will be unique but it will also show your personality, whether you are Armenian or not, whether you visited Armenia or not (yet!!!), you have here an opportunity to buy clothes that I will do only for you. This money, if the 3000 dollars goal is reached, is essential because it will allow me to create these dresses you can see on the picture (this is a prototype I am wearing). There is only one as of today. This is the same dress you will receive for 30 dollars. For 40 dollars I will do a hat for you. Don&rsquo;t forget to specify your size after the funding period is over.</p>\r\n<p>So far I do not do the shoes but I can change my mind for early backers!</p>\r\n<p>Any questions or remark, please ask me directly! Thanksdsdsahuihuihu</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '398', '{\"id\":\"398##Yerevan##AM\",\"name\":\"Yerevan, AM\"}', 'AM', '', 'no_of_days', '21', '1387381106', '', '0', '1389225599', '500', '0', '1', null, '0', '0', '0', '1387381737', '1', null, '1', '0', '1387211618', '1387380969', null, '0', '0', '0', '1387381851');
