please ask me directly!</p>\r\n<p>And THANK YOU ALL!!!! :):)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>With my clothes you will be unique!</strong></h3>\r\n<p>It will also show your personality, whether you are Armenian or not, whether you visited Armenia or not (yet!!!), you have here an opportunity to buy clothes that I will do only for you.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\r\n<li>This money, if the 3000 dollars goal is reached, is essential because it will allow me to create these dresses you can see on the picture (this is a prototype I am wearing).</li>\r\n<li>There is only one as of today. This is the same dress you will receive for 50 dollars. For 75dollars I will do a hat for you. Don&rsquo;t forget to specify your size after the funding period is over.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>So far I do not do the shoes but I can change my mind for early backers!</p>\r\n<p>Any questions or remark, please ask me directly!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '404', '{\"id\":\"404##Kapan##AM\",\"name\":\"Kapan, AM\"}', 'AM', '', 'no_of_days', '28', '1387304930', '', '0', '1389743999', '1000', '0', '1', null, '0', '0', '0', '1387306274', '1', null, '1', '0', '1387211866', '1387304771', null, '0', '0', '0', '1387306574');
INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES ('9', '8', '5', 'Your own Outfit', '', 'This what I can do for you', null, null, '', '', '', '435', '{\"id\":\"435##Maralik##AM\",\"name\":\"Maralik, AM\"}', 'AM', '', 'no_of_days', '28', null, '', '0', '1389743999', '1000', '0', '0', null, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', null, '0', '0', '1387306607', '0', null, '0', '0', '0', '1387306731');
INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES ('10', '3', '11', 'Compiling Tales from All Around the World!', 'compiling-tales-from-all-around-the-world', 'The goal of my project is to reach, move, and help people around the world, with the wisdom of the stories and tales I have compiled. For many years I have traveled and gathered many stories about personal growth and positive thinking. And I would like to share them!', 'project_1013875642832.jpg', null, '', '', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Since ancient times, parables and fables have touched the souls of many men&nbsp;and instilled wisdom into the hearts of humanity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">It&rsquo;s in these stories, that narrate experiences of life itself, where<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> the reader can relate to the main character and draw a lesson that he can apply to his daily life.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Stories are medicine for the soul</strong></em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Stories and tales are a common heritage that belongs to us all and they should not be forgotten.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">My wish is that these stories do not get lost and that we make good use of them.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>How&nbsp;did I begin&nbsp;compiling stories?</strong></em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Since I was a kid and thanks to my grandmother, I have enjoyed reading fables and tales where I learned something that helped me grow. For many years this has been my hobby: compiling these stories and travelling to hear new ones from far away countries.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>What is so special about these stories?</em></strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">These stories are a perfect teaching tool for parents, teachers, and also for coaching programs. Behind every lesson there is to learn, we find there is a story that represents and supports its essence.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Who is this project aimed at?&nbsp;</strong></em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This project is aimed at people who would like to like to surpass their selves. At people who have a difficulty and don&rsquo;t know how to overcome it. At children who without realising it, will learn invaluable lessons.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>What are my goals?</strong></em></h2>\r\n<p>The goal of this project is to raise enough funds to cover the cost of publishing a book, an eBook, launching a website and allowing me to work full time with these stories.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '398', '{\"id\":\"398##Yerevan##AM\",\"name\":\"Yerevan, AM\"}', 'AM', '', 'no_of_days', '21', '1387563922', '', '0', '1389571199', '1500', '0', '0', null, '0', '0', '1', '1387315331', '1', null, '1', '0', '1387307534', '1387315200', null, '1', '0', '0', '1389571202');
